pan class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ruby</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>拼音<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>pīnyīn<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ruby</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>运行结果: <ruby>这是<rt>zhèshì</rt></ruby><ruby>拼音<rt>pīnyīn</rt></ruby></p>\n<h2><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ruby /&gt;</code>不兼容性的回退方案<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;rp /&gt;</code></h2>\n<p>因为web标准的兼容性，<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rp\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;rp /&gt;</code></a>被用来作为<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ruby /&gt;</code>注音不支持的回退方案。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;rp /&gt;</code>的使用方法如下(需要围绕<code class=\"language-text\">rt</code>的开、闭标签):</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ruby</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n这是 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>(<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>zhèshì<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n拼音 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>(<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>pīnyīn<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ruby</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>运行结果: <ruby>这是 <rp>(</rp><rt>zhèshì</rt><rp>)</rp>拼音 <rp>(</rp><rt>pīnyīn</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></p>","excerpt":"平时浏览网页时，可以看到一些冷门、复杂单词的上方有拼音。在开发中，如何实现注音呢？ 和 MDN 说明标签 例如下面的html代码，就可以实现注音: 运行结果: 这是zhèshì拼音pīnyīn 不兼容性的回退方案 因为web…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/post/summary-2018/","title":"2018","tags":["年度","总结"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/travis/build/suyi91/suyi91.github.io/src/posts/2018-12-31---summary-2018/index.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/post/summary-2019/","title":"2019"